OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772572327
OL,3,CSchoolchildren make 2,500 flags
OL,4,Cpromoting unity following mosque arson
OL,6,FITV News Meridian's Andy Dickenson has
OL,7,Fbeen speaking to local children
OL,8,Finvolved with the community campaign.
OL,10,F2,500 posters and signs have been made
OL,11,Fby school pupils promoting unity and
OL,12,Ftolerance following an arson attack at
OL,13,Fa mosque in Sussex.
OL,15,FIt's five months since the place of
OL,16,FMuslim worship in Peacehaven came
OL,17,Funder attack, with two people having
OL,18,Fto escape from the burning building.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
