PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772572327
OL,3,CSchoolchildren make 2,500 flags
OL,4,Cpromoting unity following mosque arson
OL,6,FA police investigation resulted in
OL,7,Farrests and charges for two people who
OL,8,Fare due to stand trial on suspicion of
OL,9,Farson.
OL,11,FIn a bid to tackle division, the
OL,12,FCommunity of Kindness project has been
OL,13,Fworking with local children to create
OL,14,Fthe colourful pieces of artwork.
OL,16,FUsing words and phrases such as 'don't
OL,17,Fhate, create' and 'everybody is
OL,18,Fwelcome', the messages are being
OL,19,Fdisplayed on lamp posts and billboards
OL,20,Fin Seaford, Newhaven, Peacehaven and
OL,21,FTelscombe.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772572327
OL,3,CSchoolchildren make 2,500 flags
OL,4,Cpromoting unity following mosque arson
OL,6,FSally Franceshi, head teacher of
OL,7,FBreakwater Academy said, "I'm really
OL,8,Fproud of what our children have done
OL,9,Fas part of this project.
OL,11,F"They've really jumped on board with
OL,12,Fenthusiasm. It's about thinking about
OL,13,Fkind actions, kind words, and
OL,14,Ftolerance is really important as well
OL,15,Fbecause we don't know people.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
