FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772572327
OL,3,CSchoolchildren make 2,500 flags
OL,4,Cpromoting unity following mosque arson
OL,6,F"We don't know, where they're from,
OL,7,Ftheir cultures, their backgrounds.
OL,8,FMaybe they've got hidden disabilities
OL,9,For whatever, but it's taking people
OL,10,Ffor who they are, treating them
OL,11,Fequally, treating them fairly, and
OL,12,Fjust showing kindness to them."
OL,14,FThe project is the brains of Look
OL,15,FAgain, a socially creative initiative
OL,16,Fthat's previously delivered bright and
OL,17,Fvibrant murals in the area.
OL,19,F"This is our largest participatory art
OL,20,Fproject to date," says Charlotte
OL,21,FParsons from Look Again.
OL,26,@{D@AOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
