PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772572327
OL,3,CSchoolchildren make 2,500 flags
OL,4,Cpromoting unity following mosque arson
OL,6,F"Showing art in the public realm is
OL,7,Fabout much more than sharing space -
OL,8,Fit's an energising mix of place,
OL,9,Fpeople and creativity. "
OL,11,FCouncillor Zoe Nicholson, Leader of
OL,12,FLewes District Council, said,
OL,14,F"Seeing these vibrant posters is
OL,15,Fgenuinely uplifting. Their messages
OL,16,Ffrom the young children of respect,
OL,17,Fconsideration and kindness shine so
OL,18,Fbrightly at a time when the
OL,19,Fcommunities can feel divided.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
